 \nTopic: Clergy Day\nTime: Feb 5\, 2026 09:30 AM Pacific Time (US and Cana
 da)\nJoin Zoom Meeting\nhttps://bc-anglican-ca.zoom.us/j/84128367841\nMeet
 ing ID: 841 2836 7841\n---\nOne tap mobile\n+17789072071\,\,84128367841# C
 anada\n+14388097799\,\,84128367841# Canada\nJoin instructions\nhttps://bc-
 anglican-ca.zoom.us/meetings/84128367841/invitations?signature=KSFQO-ZG3aQ
